Doc,<br><br>
I was reading through the more intellectual parts of your <br>
post.  You indicated that the boy scouts were less than <br>
something to be proud of.  I was a really excellent Boy Scout<br>
  Learned a lot of skills and values doing that and made sure <br>
my sons had the same experience.  Learned many weapon skills<br>
which I honed later in life.  Still exceptional in the gun, bow, sling<br>
, knife, hatchet, and traps.  Suprising where you might use these<br>
skills.  Entered into a lot of campfire discussions and yes<br>
many of these had to do with God and country.  Not suprising<br>
since the association was founded by one of the best commando<br>
types.  Yes Doc these boy scouts would be a terrible example<br>
with all their &quot;BULLSHIT TALK&quot;.<br><br>
Interesting to note that you see your self as a predator who is<br>
not part of a pride.  I agree you are a worn out old predator<br>
who is asking his intended prey to kill its self.  Special, note<br>
your own words call you a &quot;predator&quot;.  These old lions are known <br>
to eat their own young.  A habit the hyena never developed.<br><br>
Beware the animal kingdom comparisons.  Few do not have purpose.<br>
  A problem that many humans do not have.
